    "Table 1 illustrates the detection result metrics for the cancer cell target detection model.",
    "The effectiveness of detecting cell images containing varying numbers of cancer cells is shown in Figure 4.",
    "These images include normal cell images, cell images with a small number of cancer cells, and cell images with a mix of several types of cancer cells among normal cells.",
